annotation_set.note:
DRAFT (pending ISBT approval) ---. Polymorphisms in LRG_806, ERMAP give rise to antigenic variants of the Scianna blood group system, SC (ISBT 013). ---. LRG t1 (NM_001017922.1) is a 12 exon model, translation initiation in exon 3. NM_018538.3 is an 11 exon model, translation initiation in exon 2. ---. It appears that NM_018538.3 (11 exons) was discovered initially, so many earlier publications (included Reid, 2) refer to variants by the exon numbering of that model (NM_018538.3/AF311285.1). Then later publications (e.g. Srivastava et al., 3) number according to 12 exons (NM_001017922.1). ---. ISBT tables (1) have listed NM_001017922.1 as the reference transcript, but described it as an 11 exon model and stated that translation initiates in exon 2, which was incorrect. In future ISBT tables NM_001017922.1 will remain as the reference transcript. ---.
REFERENCES. 1) International Society for Blood Transfusion (ISBT) allele tables, SC (ISBT 013) blood group alleles v3.0 160623 http://www.isbtweb.org/working-parties/red-cell-immunogenetics-and-blood-group-terminology/. 2) The Blood Group Antigen FactsBook, 3rd Edition, Authors: Marion Reid Christine Lomas-Francis Martin Olsson. 3) Srivastava, K et al., 2016. PMID 27612015.
